---
name: v21-native-constructor-match-guard
---

```scalascript
def classify(value: Option[Int]): String = value match
  case Some(n) if n >= 2 => "enough"
  case Some(n)           => "low"
  case None              => "missing"

println(classify(Some(3)))
println(classify(Some(1)))
println(classify(None))
```
